Some future ToDos
=================

* ARP cache poisoning for Man-In-The-Middle sniffing
* Clean and more efficient rework of netsniff-ng's packet processing machine
* Adding tons of protocols to decode
* Improvements in TX_RING/sendto PCAP replay code
* PCAPng support
* netsniff-ngd that provides network statistics for user clients (e.g. Nagios)
* Statistical anomaly detection for netsniff-ngd
* Kernelcode improvements in af_packet.c

There are also some information about future plans within our 
frequently asked questions page: http://netsniff-ng.org/faq.html
